    "Table 4 and Fig. 4 illustrate the distribution of the dataset in terms of class labels and their count.",
    "Data preprocessingData preprocessing is crucial in many ML and DL-based models for eliminating irrelevant text from the dataset, ensuring that the data are presented in a concise and appropriate format.",
